the time? Not just on Christmas?

1467
01:26:00,800 --> 01:26:09,135
Well, l guess is because...
Well, l don't know.

1468
01:26:10,471 --> 01:26:12,711
Maybe is because Christmas is like
people really

1469
01:26:12,972 --> 01:26:14,346
are and the other part ain't true.

